videos.headline: Utah State catches pick-6
videos.description: Tipa Galeai intercepts pass and returns it for a 56-yard touchdown to give Utah State a 7-0 lead against BYU.

videos.headline: Aggies convert on 4th-and-goal
videos.description: Jordan Love finds Gerold Bright wide open in the end zone on 4th-and-goal to give Utah State a 14-0 lead.

videos.headline: Utah State QB throws a dime to his WR
videos.description: Jordan Love darts it to Ron'quavion Tarver for a 6-yard score and an Aggies 21-0 lead.

videos.headline: BYU finally gets on the scoreboard
videos.description: Tanner Mangum cuts BYU's deficit down to 21-7 after a 5-yard touchdown throw.

videos.headline: BYU's Mangum scrambles and throws another TD
videos.description: Tanner Mangum connects with Dylan Collie for a 9-yard score to cut the deficit to 35-13.
